My case scenario is this
I have a navigation bar which should load another navigation bar(both navigation bars should be on my screen) which loads my content. I've been google-ing for two days i tried tons of things and none of them seem to work in my use case.
I tried using 2x router outlets(one main one with name='content'), 3x router outlets(one main one name='sidebar' one name='content'), none of them would work to load my content, i only managed to make first navigation bar to load the other navigation bar, or when clicking the second navigation bar would render my content but replaced the second navigation bar
